'''K0-B2''' was a [[Battle droid/Legends|combat droid]] abandoned when its [[Starship/Legends|starship]] was destroyed in space. It became what was commonly known as a [[Void Droid]], and patrolled the junkyards in the [[Paradise system/Legends|Paradise system]]. It carried a [[Force pike/Legends|force pike]] and a [[Blaster rifle/Legends|blaster rifle]].

